c: 7
v: 3
t: "Iti Muhammad (SAW) kuvanamati vezvidhori): “Teverai zvakadzikiswa kwamuri kubva kuna Tenzi venyu (Qur’aan ne Sunnah), uye musave munotevera maAwliya (avo vanokukurudzirai kuti muve munosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu pakunamata) kusara kwavo (Allah). Zvishoma ndizvo zvamunorangarira!”"